author: Midwinter Minis
description:
Oh would you look at what arrived in the post?

NOT SPONSORED! I paid for both of these models. Joytoy did not send them to me. I sort of wish they would though because, damn.

While I carry on building this epic MDF Ork war machine, let's quickly unbox the brand new, absolutely enormous @JoytoyOfficial #imperialknight Errant action figure.

Book me on Cameo, 100% of earnings in November getting donated to Movember: https://www.cameo.com/midwinterminis

Support us on Patreon, get a shout-out, jump on the Midwinter Minis Discord, and take part in the Painty Points competition! https://www.patreon.com/midwinterminis

Use our Wayland Games affiliate link to buy your hobby stuff at a huge discount, and we get a small kickback too! WIN WIN! https://affiliates.waylandgames.co.uk/1355-8.html
